Using 1.1.3 build, run the following fragment:

            // break out a localized Category for EMM log
            localizedCat = Category.getInstance(Constants.EMM_LOCALIZED);

            // EMM log will use localized resource bundle
            localizedCat.setResourceBundle(localizedBundle);

            // drop the SDS appenders; we want a separate log
            localizedCat.removeAllAppenders();

            // apply new EMM log appender
            PatternLayout emmLayout = new PatternLayout(EMMLAYOUT);
            String emmLogFile = System.getProperty(CATALINAHOME)+EMMLOGFILE;

            RollingFileAppender emmAppender = new RollingFileAppender
(emmLayout,emmLogFile,true);
            emmAppender.setMaxBackupIndex(3);
            localizedCat.addAppender(emmAppender);

then the localizedCat will still have its messages going to the original log as 
well as the EMM log even though removeAllAppenders was done.
